<paragraph blockId="22.[138,1185,809,908]" pageId="22" pageNumber="465">Figure 31. Map of species richness on an equal area grid map from the Worldmap program. Maximum richness shown in black and minimum in light grey, with intermediate scores grouped into grey-scale classes of approximately equal numbers of grid cells. Numbers within cells denote number of species recorded within that grid cell.</paragraph>
